---
import ApiShowcaseAnimation from "../react/animation/ApiShowcaseAnimation.jsx";
---
<section id="api" class="mt-48 mb-48 py-20 bg-black">
    <ApiShowcaseAnimation client:load />
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-10 md:mb-0 md:pr-10">
                <h2 class="api-header text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Integrasi Mudah dengan <span class="gradient-text">OpenAPI LSTM</span></h2>
                <p class="api-header-desc text-gray-400 mb-8">
                    Cukup kirim POST request dengan body JSON berisi n_days, dan API kami akan mengembalikan data dalam format JSON yang siap dipakai langsung di aplikasi atau sistem Anda.
                </p>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="api-feature flex items-start"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg><div><h4 class="font-semibold text-lg">Endpoint Simpel</h4><p class="text-gray-400">Cukup panggil `/api/v1/predict` untuk mendapatkan data harian selama 90 hari ke depan.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="api-feature flex items-start"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg><div><h4 class="font-semibold text-lg">Hanya Format JSON<h4><p class="text-gray-400">Mirip BMKG, respons API kami sepenuhnya JSON tanpa pembungkus XML atau CSV.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="api-feature flex items-start"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg><div><h4 class="font-semibold text-lg">API Dokumentasi Interaktif</h4><p class="text-gray-400">Uji endpoint dan lihat respons langsung di live demo.</p></div></div>
                </div>
                <!-- <a href="#" class="btn-primary inline-block mt-8 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-full">View API Documentation</a> -->
            </div>
            <div class="api-codeblock md:w-1/2 bg-gray-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><div class="p-4 bg-gray-900 flex items-center"><div class="flex space-x-2 mr-4"><div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div><div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div><div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div></div><div class="text-sm text-gray-400">api.hydrovision.ai/predict</div></div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <pre is:raw class="text-green-400 text-sm overflow-x-auto"><span class="text-purple-400">POST</span> <span class="text-blue-400">/api/v1/predict</span> HTTP/1.1
<span class="text-purple-400">Host:</span> api.hydrovision.ai
<span class="text-purple-400">Content-Type:</span> application/json

<span class="text-gray-500">// Response</span>
{
  <span class="text-yellow-400">"status"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">true</span>,
  <span class="text-yellow-400">"message"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"Prediksi curah hujan berhasil diambil"</span>,
  <span class="text-yellow-400">"data"</span>: [
    {
      <span class="text-yellow-400">"location"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"Gorontalo"</span>,
      <span class="text-yellow-400">"unit"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"mm/hari"</span>
      <span class="text-yellow-400">"model_used"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"lstm-v3.2.1"</span>,
      <span class="text-yellow-400">"prediction_start"</span>: <span class="text-blue-400">"2025-07-01"</span>,
      <span class="text-yellow-400">"prediction_end"</span>: <span class="text-blue-400">"2025-07-05"</span>
      <span class="text-yellow-400">"predictions"</span>: [
        {<span class="text-yellow-400">"date"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"2025-07-01"</span>,<span class="text-yellow-400">"value"</span>: <span class="text-blue-400">2.4</span>},
        {<span class="text-yellow-400">"date"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"2025-07-02"</span>,<span class="text-yellow-400">"value"</span>: <span class="text-blue-400">0</span>},
        {<span class="text-yellow-400">"date"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"2025-07-03"</span>,<span class="text-yellow-400">"value"</span>: <span class="text-blue-400">1.7</span>},
        <span class="text-gray-500">...</span>
      ]
    },
  ],
}</pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<style>
.gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #06b6d4);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
}
.btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #06b6d4);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
}
</style>